Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下该到极限了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.16,0:01:13.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚才的洞…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.75,0:01:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是村里的守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:27.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回头见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大和先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们到底是什么来头
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.13,0:01:47.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.79,0:01:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来需要增援了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上钩了 上钩了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.64,0:01:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.15,0:02:03.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是送给你们的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:06.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.95,0:02:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们是托尼卡村的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看呀 守卫的印记
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.09,0:02:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 虽然被解雇了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好像身负重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出了些小事故
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很便宜哦 新鲜出炉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.68,0:02:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快过来看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.42,0:02:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得不错吧 大丰收哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏我的技术高超呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挑选鱼饵的可是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没换鱼饵之前一无所获吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.34,0:03:02.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不太喜欢吃鱼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.48,0:03:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,法兹 别太挑剔了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.45,0:03:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃起来很麻烦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.03,0:03:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鱼腥味也大
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.93,0:03:15.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我妈在的话 就能做别的…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.63,0:03:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你妈已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.83,0:03:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在教室里也哼过这首曲子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.69,0:03:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说是听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:56.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听到的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.53,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.70,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,村里的幸存者是希塞露的熟人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.21,0:05:56.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他和我是青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.63,0:05:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩提时曾一起生活过
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.54,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直管他叫哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:02.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.65,0:06:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经好久没见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.35,0:06:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到胖成那样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是一点都没变 我就放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.65,0:06:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保护了五个孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.64,0:06:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.71,0:06:21.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从刚才就开始了 你怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得肚子里汹涌澎湃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.56,0:06:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.07,0:06:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看在不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.98,0:06:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.97,0:06:59.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.55,0:07:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.46,0:07:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个忍者护额的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是袭击村子人的同伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.38,0:07:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.51,0:07:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请等等
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是什么可疑的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.62,0:07:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险 年久失修 请勿过桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.41,0:07:40.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷欧 不行 太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.99,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是只能逃跑了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.92,0:07:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米娜 走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:26.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:07.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.57,0:09:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一时性急弄错了 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.32,0:09:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孩子们也差点因为我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.43,0:09:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露应该认识的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.85,0:09:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是多克
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.65,0:09:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾在村里担任孩子们的老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是雷欧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.83,0:09:31.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很有勇气呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.41,0:09:34.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兰德和法兹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:36.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.32,0:09:37.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.95,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是小空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.42,0:09:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:42.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.61,0:09:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有就是雷欧的妹妹米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.84,0:09:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件背心不嫌大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.07,0:09:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.26,0:09:54.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为她非常喜欢 不肯脱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以就这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.57,0:09:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.33,0:10:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 米娜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秘宝吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:20.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜为何想得到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毫无头绪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.98,0:10:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说那里到底有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.27,0:10:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾经是名学者 研究过考古学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.16,0:10:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别对巨坑进行过相当缜密的调查
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.83,0:10:42.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是关于巨坑的古文书的研究成果
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:47.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,据考证 这里面记录了某个历史事件
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上古之神创造的天之矛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被污秽之人夺去了力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因污秽之人憎恨一切事物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.64,0:11:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,企图利用那份力量毁灭世界
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.29,0:11:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那股足以颠覆世界的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就要将世界毁于一旦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个亡灵偶然捡到了力量的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.81,0:11:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化身为身覆赤炎者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.77,0:11:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,向污秽之人复仇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:28.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,经过七度炼狱的激战之后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.57,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身覆赤炎者最终获胜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.69,0:11:37.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,赤炎者为防其他污秽之人玷污力量
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.37,0:11:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将其分为七个音符并封印在这段音律里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.87,0:11:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以上就是简要的概括
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,音律…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.61,0:11:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是兜偷的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.26,0:11:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果确实存在的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.39,0:11:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天之矛到底是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.27,0:12:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我认为那是超越人类智慧的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.39,0:12:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实能感觉到那个巨坑中藏有什么重大的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:18.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,且不说盗取秘宝的恶行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.45,0:12:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连无辜的村民都赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.30,0:12:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种事绝不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.27,0:12:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身有同感
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会让兜偿还所有的罪孽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.30,0:12:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.69,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.91,0:13:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家准备一起去泡露天温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.56,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和小樱混浴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.19,0:13:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.68,0:13:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.40,0:13:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是传说中的英雄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们进行修炼后 或许也能做到哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.48,0:13:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.57,0:13:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人在这种乡下地方也是名人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.98,0:13:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本以为是个相当强势可怕的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.34,0:13:56.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到既年轻又随和 让人大吃一惊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.89,0:14:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个身体里蕴藏着相当了不起的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.87,0:14:05.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一般大时
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没能救起一个女生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.09,0:14:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希塞露 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.48,0:14:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这道伤疤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很久以前从悬崖下摔了下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.92,0:14:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概有50米高
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.42,0:14:34.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好挂在树上得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.39,0:14:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.79,0:14:44.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 希塞露
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.75,0:14:46.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看招
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥反复叮嘱我小心些
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.21,0:14:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.19,0:14:59.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时他立刻抓住了我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.93,0:15:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概有一小时左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直抓着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.47,0:15:09.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我不爱运动 缺乏腕力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很丢脸 很后悔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果希塞露死了的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.04,0:15:42.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是哥哥的责任
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.36,0:15:45.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讨厌如此懦弱的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.76,0:15:47.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦成为了一名守卫
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.71,0:15:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此付出了努力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.33,0:15:51.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是不太适合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就各奔东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:59.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔去看他 总觉得有些尴尬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知不觉就疏远了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果那晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.17,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违的重聚 虽然很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.37,0:16:21.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拥有更强大的力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更强…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥肯定很懊恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.77,0:16:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能救更多人了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失去了那么多重要的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:56.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.69,0:16:57.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,办不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.32,0:17:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人哥哥 告诉我们诀窍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:23.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在我打算睡觉时发觉了村子的异常
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.19,0:17:32.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一瞬间 村子便成了火海
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.17,0:17:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也被忍者袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对手太强了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我以为自己死定了的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进攻突然停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:57.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如同断线的木偶一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.56,0:18:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,秽土转生这种忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.43,0:18:01.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以活人充当祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.12,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将死者的灵魂束缚其中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.20,0:18:06.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并强制将其唤醒的禁术
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.31,0:18:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原以为只有第二代火影和大蛇丸会使用
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.73,0:18:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙还不能百分之百成功地控制晓的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.95,0:18:19.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来忍术不够成熟…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.26,0:18:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多克先生知道音律吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.70,0:18:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古文书提到的那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来兜的目标是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有关音律 您知道些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.05,0:18:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者有供参考的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带上这个快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随你把它扔在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但绝不可泄露此事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.54,0:18:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.33,0:18:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天起 我们将和镇里的警卫队合作
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.55,0:18:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搜寻那个家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然有守卫被抓的先例
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.60,0:19:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会在您身边安排护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.97,0:19:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.28,0:19:10.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有那些得救的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇上的福利院愿意接收他们
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:17.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.90,0:19:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡得很熟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.62,0:19:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 这些孩子笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.48,0:19:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天夜里以来 第一次…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:19:58.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:02.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你设计的术式真够乱来的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.55,0:20:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明不用赶尽杀绝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.90,0:20:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有你这么觉得吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.78,0:20:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大蛇丸肯定会这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.74,0:20:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我用自己的查克拉改良了术式
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.41,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次一定能成功控制
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.87,0:20:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该试试拥有意识和记忆的状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.12,0:20:29.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些东西还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.30,0:20:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许被谁拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:36.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又要让我去找吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当初不是这么决定的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很会使唤人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了 也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉越来越有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.40,0:20:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鸣人…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.85,0:22:41.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,好寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.09,0:22:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,好孤单啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.11,0:22:44.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,怎么会寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.33,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,一直都在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.22,0:22:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,下集 火影忍者疾风传
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.52,0:23:00.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,5,,力量 第三集

